title: Travel update: Accident involving two lorries on A303 | Meridian
text:
Queueing traffic and road closed due to accident, two lorries involved on A303 Westbound between A338 (Parkhouse Cross) and A345 Countess Road (Countess Roundabout).
Affecting traffic between Andover and Amesbury.
Last updated Tue 8 Sep 2015 Travel Hampshire & Isle of Wight Wiltshire
